                <h3>Pre-Purchase Your Baggage Allowance</h3>
                <p>Suppose you pre-purchase your baggage allowance or add your baggage during the time of booking or a flight ticket purchase or at least 24 hours before your flight to save money. This is the right move for buying your baggage allowance in advance because baggage allowance at the airport is very expensive.</p>
